            Riboflavin 1% + Dextra¬n 20% drops was administrated on the cornea for 30 minutes the cornea was exposed to ultraviolet light using UV-X machine for 10 minutes power
            @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.oclt_3, new { @class = "form-control-sm", @width = "20px", @id = "uoclt_3", @maxlength = "250" })mj.
        </div>
